gv(tasker/hactrl) = light.turn_on&{ "entity_id": "light.bedroom_lights", "brightness": 30 }

URI Format:
tasker://secondary?service=var&json={ var }

Combined:
tasker://secondary?service=light.turn_on&json={ "entity_id": "light.bedroom_lights", "brightness": 30 }


-- NEW
Kustom Global data:
light_on&light.bedroom_lights&brightness:255

URI Format:
tasker://secondary?service_call=var&entity_id=var&parameters=var:100

Combined:
tasker://secondary?service_call=light_on&entity_id=light.bedroom_lights&parameters=brightness:125

